+## Architecture
+
+```
+  Phone / Browser
+        |
+        | HTTP/JSON (LAN only)
+        v
+  Zend Home Miner Daemon
+    |
+    +--> Event Spine (append-only encrypted journal)
+    |         |
+    |         +--> Operations Inbox (derived view)
+    |
+    +--> Miner Simulator (phase 1)
+              |
+              v
+         Zcash Network (future)
+
+  Hermes Adapter --> Hermes Gateway (future)
+```
+
+The daemon exposes a LAN-only HTTP API. The command center is a single HTML file
+that polls this API and renders the mobile-first UI.
+
